				</p>
				<blockquote>
					The mission of <i>FIRST</i> is to inspire young people to be science and technology leaders, by engaging them in exciting Mentor-based programs that build science, engineering, and technology skills, that inspire innovation, and that foster well-rounded life capabilities including self-confidence, communication, and leadership.
					<cite><i>FIRST</i> Mission Statement</cite>
				</blockquote>
				<p>
